item.description: Songs: Saki Kaskamanidis: Little Sweaty Sow, Changes, Fast Lane, Prime Funk (Extended), Feta Cheese, Globular Cluster, Siwash Rock, Knossos (Remix), Saturnight, Callista, Bulbular Swirl, Fasolatha, Nashat, Powerslide, Amorphous Being, Showcase, Toxic Exhaust, Flimsy, Gore, Bleary Playlist Title: Saki Kaskamanidis Notes Saki was straight-up a monster talent, and humble, and authentic.
